<TEXT>
WEDNESDAY:
For four days Epsom Downs, just outside London, will be covered in Fortnum
and Mason hampers, marquees, a fun-fair and gipsy caravans. The Epsom
meeting opens with Derby day and finishes on Saturday, when the Oaks race
for fillies will be run.
