England take on New Zealand in the first cricket Test at Trent Bridge. After
his ordeal against the West Indian fast bowlers over the winter, Mike
Atherton will start his first full home series as England captain more
worried about bouncers from the selection committee than on the pitch. New
Zealand, for all their youthful promise, are one of the weaker cricket
nations.
